                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080914-2-off6 t18080914-2-cd7"></join>, and stealing therein one gown, value 12 s. two petticoats, value 12 s. and a pair of breeches, value 20 s. the property of the said 
