            . I live at <placeName id="t18080914-2-crimeloc8">No. 35, Hare street, Bethnal Green</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18080914-2-crimeloc8" type="placeName" value="No. 35, Hare street, Bethnal Green"></interp>
